            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/daphne_bavelier_825088",
        "quote": "We know there are good sugars and bad sugars, and we don't discuss whether food in general is good or bad for us. We need to be far more nuanced when we talk about the effects of video games.",
