            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/daphne_bavelier_825084",
        "quote": "'Screen time' is meaningless - what matters is what you do while on the screen. The good, the bad, and the ugly faces of screen time will all have to do with which activities you engage into.",
