                "url": "/topics/instance"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/daphne_bavelier_825081",
        "quote": "We have a large amount of data that shows playing fast-paced games improves hand-eye co-ordination, the ability to focus on the task at hand, and your ability to make decisions, as gaming improves your brain's allocation of resources.",
