            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/daphne_bavelier_825086",
        "quote": "In order to sharpen its prediction skills, our brains constantly build models, or 'templates,' of the world. The better the template, the better the performance. And now we know playing action video game actually fosters better templates.",
